{"tid":1022743,"cid":27,"subCid":0,"title":"[TG] 深度電影討論台","createTime":"2019-02-15T08:37:42.000Z","updateTime":"2019-04-26T13:18:46.000Z","uid":34567,"like":4,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"3b6a06d4d113d373ac3d9957f06b0be5c3f1bafe","tid":1022743,"uid":34567,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-15T08:37:42.000Z","msg":"小弟知道好多人都想有個地方可以好好討論電影，同接觸更多不同類型既電影，但奈何好多時入左啲所謂電影吹水台都變左普通吹水台，真正講電影既少之又少<br />\n<br />\n有見及此，小弟就開左個TG gp，一心聚集一班醉心於電影既同好，召集所有愛好的電影既各位<br />\n<br />\n為左確保本群唔淪為無聊吹水台，為大家提供一個只討論電影既平台，所以麻煩大家花少少時間答幾條非常簡單既問題，唔該晒～<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://docs.google.com/forms/d/e/1FAIpQLSd5KwSKSjWkir86hFauxMTXderlo_XVIGCHGRHmWzl3hveFkg/viewform?usp=sf_link\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fdocs.google.com%2Fforms%2Fd%2Fe%2F1FAIpQLSd5KwSKSjWkir86hFauxMTXderlo_XVIGCHGRHmWzl3hveFkg%2Fviewform%3Fusp%3Dsf_link&d=rje4l1xmTn6y9o%2BHBfPaf85Q2JFdPMmcxM5Tq6mQO7A%3D&h=800f6685\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://docs.google.com/forms/d/e/1FAIpQLSd5KwSKSjWkir86hFauxMTXderlo_XVIGCHGRHmWzl3hveFkg/viewform?usp=sf_link</a>"},{"pid":"a39478662a8a243bda01c4c7bbacc9abb89f5f39","tid":1022743,"uid":116725,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-15T10:40:00.000Z","msg":"正喎～"},{"pid":"874979760497df102b71f852aa6fb4eda7efa642","tid":1022743,"uid":128220,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-15T10:59:44.000Z","msg":"ok"},{"pid":"5530412bd8dffae0b17f8ad2ef63b7fbad56a444","tid":1022743,"uid":121740,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-15T11:10:30.000Z","msg":"noted with thanks"},{"pid":"8d4cb04f4b6233a9d7c6aa9f34242d1a585dea83","tid":1022743,"uid":34567,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-16T01:27:49.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/05.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9a184147d89a03de99abd0a7a3f042cc8eaa5584","tid":1022743,"uid":34567,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-17T